{"lastModified":1772715993230,"uri":"c::30234707298::vessel::0203d530-f527-11ef-8367-919d81efba36","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Croatia, Montenegro\n\nLagoon 46 Naya is a brand-new, state-of-the-art sailing catamaran designed for an unparalleled luxury sailing experience in Croatia. Based in the Dubrovnik region at ACI Marina Dubrovnik, this elegant catamaran offers private charters for smaller groups of up to 8 guests, making it perfect for family vacations, celebrations, or intimate getaways.\n\nBuilt by the renowned Lagoon Catamarans, Lagoon 46 Naya is equipped with the latest amenities to ensure comfort and style at sea. The catamaran features four spacious double cabins, each with en-suite bathrooms, providing privacy and relaxation for all guests. The vessel is operated by a professional two-member crew, including a skilled skipper and a chef/steward, who ensure a seamless and personalized experience throughout your journey.\n\nOnboard, you’ll find expansive sun decks with a seating area at the front, a cockpit dining area at the back for al fresco meals, and an elegant indoor saloon with a smartly designed galley and additional dining space. Every detail has been carefully thought out to combine luxury, comfort, and functionality, creating the perfect setting for your sailing adventure in Lagoon 46 Croatia.\n\nYour charter aboard Lagoon 46 Naya offers a customized itinerary, allowing you to explore Croatia’s stunning Adriatic coastline, hidden bays, and picturesque islands at your own pace. Whether you’re sunbathing on the deck, savoring freshly prepared meals, or swimming in turquoise waters, this catamaran promises an unforgettable experience.","blueprint":{"name":"NAYA","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::0203d530-f527-11ef-8367-919d81efba36::assets::2088c301-f52a-11ef-84e3-b5d14125561a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::0203d530-f527-11ef-8367-919d81efba36::assets::208a97c0-f52a-11ef-84e3-b5d14125